# =======================================================
# --- GUIDE: HOW TO IGNORE OTHER ITEMS ---
# (Add your own rules below)
# =======================================================

# TO IGNORE WHOLE FOLDERS:
# Write the folder name followed by a slash /
# Example: output_data/
# Example: logs/

# TO IGNORE FILE EXTENSIONS:
# Use the asterisk * as a wildcard
# Example: *.csv       (Ignores all CSVs, useful for data)
# Example: *.log       (Ignores log files)
# Example: *.tmp       (Ignores temporary files)

# TO IGNORE A SPECIFIC FILE:
# Write the exact name
# Example: config.json (If it contains API keys)
# Example: .env        (For secret environment variables)

